28
00:02:28,870 --> 00:02:32,989
His mom throws me a party every year

29
00:02:32,990 --> 00:02:35,039
and he's forced to attend.

30
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:39,539
But I want him to
want to celebrate my birthday!

31
