34
00:02:49,620 --> 00:02:53,329
I' d be fine with a super
expensive present.

35
00:02:53,330 --> 00:02:54,989
You' re so materialistic.

36
00:02:54,990 --> 00:02:57,329
Why don' t you ask for a present?

37
00:02:57,330 --> 00:03:00,539
A super expensive one!

38
00:03:00,540 --> 00:03:05,050
It' s not the price!
A gift should be heartfelt.

39
00:03:05,450 --> 00:03:07,990
What has he given you so far?

40
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:11,039
What has he given me? Well...

41
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:12,459
Tell us! Tell us!

42
00:03:12,460 --> 00:03:15,630
Tell us what he gave you!

43
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:19,640
Hm? Huh?

44
00:03:19,990 --> 00:03:24,220
Wait a minute. he' s never...

45
00:03:24,990 --> 00:03:29,449
He' s never given me a present.

46
00:03:29,450 --> 00:03:30,990
No way!

47
00:03:31,450 --> 00:03:34,040
How many years
have you been married?

48
00:03:34,660 --> 00:03:35,989
I can' t believe it.

49
00:03:35,990 --> 00:03:37,929
Poor Kotoko.

50
00:03:37,930 --> 00:03:39,989
This calls for a divorce!

51
00:03:39,990 --> 00:03:43,270
He doesn' t love you at all!

52
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:47,949
That' s not true! He' s
just a little shy...

53
00:03:47,950 --> 00:03:50,109
