54
00:03:50,110 --> 00:03:51,419
Here is a problem.

55
00:03:51,420 --> 00:03:52,950
Is there another woman?

56
00:03:53,830 --> 00:03:55,080
Fine!

57
00:03:55,340 --> 00:04:00,249
This year, it will be roses
and champagne and...

58
00:04:00,250 --> 00:04:05,120
a heartfelt present.
I will make it come true!

59
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:06,579
1,000 yen that it doesn? t.

60
00:04:06,580 --> 00:04:08,119
Me, too. 1,000yen.

61
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,789
Count me in. 1,000yen.

62
00:04:09,790 --> 00:04:13,130
Doesn' t anyone have faith?

63
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:13,990
Final Episode
Best Birthday Gift Ever

64
00:06:15,460 --> 00:06:16,490
The 28th?

65
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,720
Yes!

66
00:06:19,670 --> 00:06:22,390
I have surgery and night duty.

67
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:24,920
Was there something else?

68
00:06:26,290 --> 00:06:29,610
He doesn' t remember...

69
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:34,630
Never mind.

70
00:06:36,170 --> 00:06:41,110
I won' t give up! This calls for...

71
