There you are, Mr. Irie!

72
00:06:48,290 --> 00:06:49,810
What' s with you?

73
00:06:50,090 --> 00:06:51,760
Oh, it' s you, Funatsu.

74
00:06:53,210 --> 00:06:56,520
I' ll take your shift on the 28th.

75
00:06:57,610 --> 00:06:58,610
Huh?

76
00:06:59,210 --> 00:07:01,479
On the 28th...

77
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,510
I don' t need to switch shifts.

78
00:07:04,380 --> 00:07:05,380
Huh?

79
00:07:06,050 --> 00:07:08,369
 But you have to!
- Huh?

80
00:07:08,370 --> 00:07:10,379
You have to switch with me!

81
00:07:10,380 --> 00:07:12,810
Or else Kotoko... Oops.

82
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:16,680
Why do I have to?

83
00:07:17,290 --> 00:07:19,400
No...

84
00:07:20,710 --> 00:07:22,629
What did Kotoko tell you?

85
00:07:22,630 --> 00:07:25,060
No... nothing...

86
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,360
Funatsu!

87
00:07:28,860 --> 00:07:32,290
Kotoko said if I switch shifts
with you on the 28th

88
00:07:32,300 --> 00:07:35,530
she' ll arrange a date for me
with Miss Marina.

89
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:37,290
A date?

90
00:07:37,291 --> 00:07:41,380
So please let me
take your shift on the 28th!

91
00:07:42,210 --> 00:07:43,500
That' s a promise!

92
00:07:45,290 --> 00:07:47,250
What' s with Funatsu?

93
00:07:54,250 --> 00:07:56,169
Just you and Naoki?

94
00:07:56,170 --> 00:07:57,919
I' m sorry...

95
00:07:57,920 --> 00:08:01,289
I' m so sad!

96
00:08:01,290 --> 00:08:04,499
I was looking forward to this event!

97
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:07,299
The banner is almost finished.

98
00:08:07,300 --> 00:08:08,689
Banner?

99
00:08:08,690 --> 00:08:09,690
See?

100
00:08:10,610 --> 00:08:13,040
I' m sorry...

101
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:17,089
We can have a party...

102
00:08:17,090 --> 00:08:18,280
No!

103
00:08:18,290 --> 00:08:21,130
You' re absolutely right!

104
00:08:21,780 --> 00:08:24,339
Naoki hates our parties.

105
00:08:24,340 --> 00:08:27,420
He acts like he' s forced to be there!

106
00:08:27,850 --> 00:08:30,670
I' ve never seen him give you a present.

107
00:08:32,590 --> 00:08:34,290
All right, Kotoko!

108
00:08:35,070 --> 00:08:39,250
You and Naoki should spend some
quality time together this year.

109
00:08:39,800 --> 00:08:43,420
I' ll swallow my tears this time...

110
00:08:44,670 --> 00:08:45,970
Mom...

111
00:08:47,490 --> 00:08:51,629
Let' s put up a plan for this, Kotoko!

112
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:52,630
Okay!

113
00:08:53,050 --> 00:08:55,920
How can we drop subtle hints

114
00:08:56,210 --> 00:08:59,780
so Naoki will remember your birthday?

115
00:09:00,210 --> 00:09:01,290
Yes...

116
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:03,670
Subtle hints won' t work.

117
00:09:05,580 --> 00:09:06,580
What?

118
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:10,000
You were scheming with Funatsu today.

119
00:09:11,170 --> 00:09:14,420
Funatsu... that big mouth!

120
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:17,290
So, your birthday is coming up.

121
00:09:18,300 --> 00:09:20,870
Mom gets excited every year.

122
00:09:22,510 --> 00:09:25,040
But I have no interest in birthdays.

123
00:09:26,290 --> 00:09:29,959
Naoki, you' re terrible!

124
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:34,360
You have no interest in
your beloved wife' s birthday?

125
00:09:35,350 --> 00:09:39,720
Do you want to celebrate
your birthday that badly?

126
00:09:41,290 --> 00:09:44,300
It was my lifelong dream...

127
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:47,040
I see...

128
00:09:49,770 --> 00:09:53,600
What kind of birthday
is your lifelong dream?

129
00:09:54,170 --> 00:09:57,170
Tell him, Kotoko!

130
00:09:58,330 --> 00:10:00,129
It' s embarrassing...

131
00:10:00,130 --> 00:10:01,610
I just...

132
00:10:02,710 --> 00:10:05,120
I would get all dressed up.

133
00:10:06,490 --> 00:10:12,520
Naoki would give me
a huge bouquet of roses.

134
00:10:21,900 --> 00:10:23,400
We' d have dinner...

135
00:10:24,140 --> 00:10:27,840
The chef would bring us a cake.

136
00:10:28,810 --> 00:10:33,380
Everyone would sing
Happy birthday to me.

137
00:10:41,820 --> 00:10:47,290
We would sip champagne...

138
00:10:49,060 --> 00:10:51,960
And spend the evening together...

139
00:10:59,810 --> 00:11:03,880
I see how important this is to you.

140
00:11:04,970 --> 00:11:05,970
Huh?

141
00:11:06,590 --> 00:11:10,280
I' ll switch shifts with Funatsu
on the 28th.

142
00:11:11,140 --> 00:11:13,350
Rea... really?

143
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:17,160
Are you sure?

144
00:11:17,510 --> 00:11:20,590
Yeah. He can be a pest, too.

145
00:11:22,100 --> 00:11:23,930
Yay!

146
00:11:29,890 --> 00:11:32,350
You did it, Kotoko!

147
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:34,850
Yay! Naoki!

148
00:11:38,220 --> 00:11:43,429
From the day I met Naoki...

149
00:11:43,430 --> 00:11:46,050
I dreamed of a birthday like this...

150
00:11:51,430 --> 00:11:55,730
My birthday finally came.

151
00:12:00,510 --> 00:12:02,370
Don' t forget, Naoki!

152
00:12:02,590 --> 00:12:05,270
7:00pm at the Royal Hotel lobby!

153
00:12:05,510 --> 00:12:06,510
Yeah.

154
00:12:06,590 --> 00:12:08,590
Remember, Naoki.

155
00:12:09,030 --> 00:12:12,600
I gave up my party plan for Kotoko

156
00:12:12,800 --> 00:12:13,800
Yeah.

157
00:12:14,590 --> 00:12:19,639
I don' t need a bouquet of roses...
It's ok...

158
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:20,590
Yeah!

159
00:12:20,591 --> 00:12:24,049
I really don' t! Not at all.

160
00:12:24,050 --> 00:12:27,130
Give me a break! Enough already!

161
00:12:27,760 --> 00:12:29,100
Poor Naoki.

162
00:12:31,140 --> 00:12:32,460
A little...

163
00:12:33,590 --> 00:12:34,590
See you.

164
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:35,530
Hair Salon at 15:30pm

165
00:13:41,341 --> 00:13:44,081
I' d better get ready, too.

166
00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:46,282
Put on my beautiful dress...

167
00:13:46,509 --> 00:13:48,355
and get my hair done

168
00:13:48,380 --> 00:13:49,384
into a beautiful hair style.

169
00:13:49,869 --> 00:13:52,463
And my make-up, too...

170
00:13:53,281 --> 00:13:55,233
This is a special day.

171
00:13:55,885 --> 00:13:59,347
I' m going all out!

172
00:14:01,606 --> 00:14:05,213
He may fall in love with me
all over again!

173
00:14:24,155 --> 00:14:27,944
Mom, her hair looks like a cockatoo.

174
00:14:27,969 --> 00:14:29,239


175
00:14:31,716 --> 00:14:32,859
This is terrible!

176
00:14:33,883 --> 00:14:37,443
What is this hair style?

177
00:14:38,952 --> 00:14:43,575
Maybe I should do it over!
But I don' t have time.

178
00:14:43,842 --> 00:14:48,285
Maybe it' s not as bad as I think...

179
00:14:54,778 --> 00:14:58,988
Why couldn' t I tell him
I didn' t like it?

180
00:14:59,377 --> 00:15:01,417
I' m so stupid...

181
00:15:03,589 --> 00:15:04,545
What' s wrong?

182
00:15:04,716 --> 00:15:05,513
Are you okay?

183
00:15:10,533 --> 00:15:11,548
What' s wrong?

184
00:15:11,939 --> 00:15:15,005
She started wavering and
she doubled over.

185
00:15:15,973 --> 00:15:18,132
She collapsed and hit her head!

186
00:15:21,043 --> 00:15:22,511
Are you okay?

187
00:15:24,439 --> 00:15:26,469
Let' s put your head up a little, ok?

188
00:15:28,487 --> 00:15:29,487
Okay.

189
00:15:31,571 --> 00:15:34,251
Does anyone have a handkerchief?

190
00:15:35,288 --> 00:15:36,702
Here, use this.

191
00:15:36,803 --> 00:15:37,963
Thank you.

192
00:15:39,267 --> 00:15:41,751
Can you call an ambulance?

193
00:15:41,796 --> 00:15:42,432
Sure!

194
00:15:42,457 --> 00:15:43,457
Okay.

195
00:15:44,740 --> 00:15:47,760
Can I borrow your bag?

196
00:15:47,785 --> 00:15:48,625
Sure.

197
00:15:48,650 --> 00:15:50,429
Place it under her head.

198
00:15:54,704 --> 00:15:56,410
Is she a nurse?

199
00:15:57,156 --> 00:15:58,826
I thought she was a barmaid.

200
00:15:59,255 --> 00:16:01,267
The ambulance will be here soon.

201
00:16:01,561 --> 00:16:02,967
Can you say your name?

202
00:16:04,039 --> 00:16:06,669
Does it hurt anywhere else?

203
00:16:10,389 --> 00:16:13,838
She' s lucky you were a nurse.

204
00:16:14,017 --> 00:16:17,267
I think it' s anemia,
but she was also bleeding...

205
00:16:19,055 --> 00:16:20,087
Thank you very much.

206
00:16:20,530 --> 00:16:21,776
You did a great job.

207
00:16:21,895 --> 00:16:23,180
Good job, lady.

208
00:16:23,205 --> 00:16:24,593
Terrific.

209
00:16:24,618 --> 00:16:26,420
Very cool.

210
00:16:28,569 --> 00:16:30,521
Not really...

211
00:16:34,042 --> 00:16:35,496


212
00:16:35,693 --> 00:16:37,103
Just leave it there.

213
00:16:37,793 --> 00:16:39,373


214
00:16:39,438 --> 00:16:41,079
I was just passing by.

215
00:16:41,583 --> 00:16:44,113
She' s not my friend...

216
00:16:44,249 --> 00:16:46,869
Let me out!

217
00:16:53,629 --> 00:16:57,719
What should I do?
I' m over two hours late.

218
00:16:58,327 --> 00:17:00,929
Naoki may have already left.

219
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:04,730
Why today...

220
00:17:08,617 --> 00:17:11,397
Sorry, Naoki!

221
00:17:12,287 --> 00:17:14,807
Please wait...

222
00:17:16,362 --> 00:17:17,902
a little longer!

223
00:17:33,159 --> 00:17:34,159
Ma' am.

224
00:17:34,869 --> 00:17:38,659
What happened to your dress?

225
00:17:39,526 --> 00:17:41,248
What do you mean?

226
00:17:41,273 --> 00:17:43,023
Are you hurt?

227
00:17:44,862 --> 00:17:47,032
This is... oh no!

228
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:50,712
What should I do?

229
00:17:51,001 --> 00:17:51,650
Ma' am?

230
00:17:51,786 --> 00:17:55,126
I can' t see Naoki like this...

231
00:17:55,428 --> 00:17:58,437
I was supposed
to meet someone here...

232
00:17:58,462 --> 00:18:01,911
But I' m already 3 hours late...

233
00:18:02,048 --> 00:18:04,458
Shall I call him?

234
00:18:05,026 --> 00:18:06,514
It' s my birthday...

235
00:18:07,862 --> 00:18:11,559
I can' t see Naoki like this...

236
00:18:12,545 --> 00:18:13,831
Ma' am...

237
00:18:15,156 --> 00:18:19,276
It's my first birthday with him...

238
00:18:20,136 --> 00:18:22,686
I can' t see him like this!

239
00:18:23,460 --> 00:18:26,775
Why not wait over there?

240
00:18:26,966 --> 00:18:29,526
Did he go home already?

241
00:18:31,011 --> 00:18:34,781
I have no idea, ma' am.

242
00:18:42,702 --> 00:18:43,882
Naoki?

243
00:18:45,110 --> 00:18:47,540
I thought you were hurt...

244
00:18:48,809 --> 00:18:51,599
You scared me.

245
00:18:54,912 --> 00:18:56,432
Naoki!

246
00:18:58,297 --> 00:19:02,217
I' m sorry... I m so late...

247
00:19:04,115 --> 00:19:08,085
A lot happened and
I couldn' t get here...

248
00:19:12,914 --> 00:19:15,439
I was going crazy...

249
00:19:17,662 --> 00:19:22,061
I thought you' d already left...

250
00:19:23,597 --> 00:19:26,917
But I couldn' t give up

251
00:19:30,081 --> 00:19:33,311
I knew you' d get here today,

252
00:19:33,931 --> 00:19:36,381
even if you had to crawl all the way...

253
00:19:36,746 --> 00:19:38,436
How could I leave?

254
00:19:40,582 --> 00:19:43,622
But you look a mess.

255
00:19:45,078 --> 00:19:46,588
I know...

256
00:19:48,143 --> 00:19:51,043
You can tell me about it later...

257
00:19:52,418 --> 00:19:53,658
I' m hungry.

258
00:19:56,389 --> 00:19:59,039
The restaurant is closed...

259
00:19:59,426 --> 00:20:01,066
And the way you look...

260
00:20:01,952 --> 00:20:04,662
Hey, guy!

261
00:20:06,483 --> 00:20:07,683
Hi!

262
00:20:08,802 --> 00:20:13,251
You dropped your package.

263
00:20:13,528 --> 00:20:16,461
Someone will steal it
if you leave it there.

264
00:20:16,566 --> 00:20:19,466
Here you go. Hold it.

265
00:20:19,933 --> 00:20:22,095
Oh, no!

266
00:20:22,266 --> 00:20:26,006
I have to catch a plane
back to my home country.

267
00:20:27,959 --> 00:20:31,938
Good luck, you two!

268
00:20:32,159 --> 00:20:33,779
See you!

269
00:20:48,962 --> 00:20:50,292
How pretty.

270
00:20:50,986 --> 00:20:53,576
A rose for every year.

271
00:20:56,053 --> 00:20:59,043
And there' s cake. Let' s eat it.

272
00:21:01,983 --> 00:21:04,683
What was my mom thinking?

273
00:21:06,423 --> 00:21:09,284
What am I going to do with this?

274
00:21:09,667 --> 00:21:10,763
Mom...

275
00:21:11,078 --> 00:21:15,458
I wonder if she was
secretly waiting for me?

276
00:21:16,060 --> 00:21:20,340
Probably. With her video camera.

277
00:21:21,134 --> 00:21:24,134
She has so much time on her hands.

278
00:21:24,689 --> 00:21:27,939
But I' m so happy.

279
00:21:29,390 --> 00:21:33,130
I' m the luckiest wife in the world.

280
00:21:35,014 --> 00:21:38,064
Happy birthday, Kotoko.

281
00:21:39,603 --> 00:21:41,263
Naoki...

282
00:21:41,648 --> 00:21:43,438
What do you want for a present?

283
00:21:44,582 --> 00:21:46,791
